#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:2
#: c9fb6fb8ffb64b4b9df4ccf7df21811a
msgid "Plasticity (J2 with Isotropic Hardening)"
msgstr "塑性（带各向同性硬化的 J2）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:4
#: d4a77cc050de4ba2b750e50bd16315cf
msgid ""
"A plane-strain plasticity problem: a :math:`1.0 \\times 0.2` m steel strip "
"is stretched 10 % then unloaded, exhibiting the characteristic permanent "
"(plastic) deformation that the elastic solver in :doc:`cantilever_beam` "
"cannot capture. The script "
"``examples/solid/plasticity_strip/plasticity_strip.py`` uses J2 flow theory "
"with linear isotropic hardening, integrated in a **variational constitutive "
"update** style — the constitutive response is encoded as an algorithmic "
"potential, the displacement update is one L-BFGS pass, and history variables"
" are advanced once per converged step."
msgstr ""
"一个平面应变塑性问题：一根 :math:`1.0 \\times 0.2` m 的钢条被拉伸 10 % 然后卸载，表现出特征性的永久（塑性）变形——这是"
" :doc:`cantilever_beam` 中的弹性求解器无法捕捉的。脚本 "
"``examples/solid/plasticity_strip/plasticity_strip.py`` 采用带线性各向同性硬化的 J2 "
"流动理论，以 **变分本构更新** 的方式积分——本构响应被编码为一个算法势，位移更新是一次 L-BFGS 过程，历史变量在每个收敛步推进一次。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:15
#: 00e29d849bce4f4ab2e904b116c25ce2
msgid ""
"The constitutive model is dimension-generic, so the same "
":class:`~tensormesh.assemble.J2Plasticity` runs unchanged in 3D — see `Going"
" to 3D`_ at the end of this page."
msgstr ""
"本构模型是维度无关的，因此同一个 :class:`~tensormesh.assemble.J2Plasticity` "
"在三维中也能原封不动地运行——参见本页末尾的 `Going to 3D`_\\ 。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:21
#: 084f9279217f406abb6486ded9b74427
msgid "Problem"
msgstr "问题"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:23
#: ebeda03b1d834cffa6b57abc2e550c42
msgid ""
"Small-strain elastoplasticity. The Cauchy stress is the elastic response of "
"the **elastic** part of the strain:"
msgstr "小应变弹塑性。柯西应力是应变的 **弹性** 部分所对应的弹性响应："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:26
#: 33965bdadfd04ce5bc033e6acfa92e03
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"\\boldsymbol{\\sigma} \\;=\\;\n"
"\\mathbb{C} : (\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon} - \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}^p),"
msgstr ""
"\\boldsymbol{\\sigma} \\;=\\;\n"
"\\mathbb{C} : (\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon} - \\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}^p),"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:31
#: 04ff6d86d98343f380160b3a63047ed2
msgid "with yield surface"
msgstr "其屈服面为"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:33
#: 2e84b883a8664ac69eb4814f80f136a5
msgid ""
"f(\\boldsymbol{\\sigma}, \\alpha)\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"\\|\\,\\mathrm{dev}\\, \\boldsymbol{\\sigma}\\,\\|\n"
"- \\sqrt{\\tfrac{2}{3}} \\bigl(\\sigma_y + H\\, \\alpha\\bigr),"
msgstr ""
"f(\\boldsymbol{\\sigma}, \\alpha)\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"\\|\\,\\mathrm{dev}\\, \\boldsymbol{\\sigma}\\,\\|\n"
"- \\sqrt{\\tfrac{2}{3}} \\bigl(\\sigma_y + H\\, \\alpha\\bigr),"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:40
#: 412cfa9d00cf40dd8d9d4febb4fd921c
msgid ""
"evolution :math:`\\dot{\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}}^p = \\dot\\gamma\\, "
"\\mathbf{n}`, :math:`\\dot\\alpha = \\sqrt{\\tfrac{2}{3}}\\, \\dot\\gamma`. "
"Material: :math:`E = 200` GPa, :math:`\\nu = 0.3`, :math:`\\sigma_y = 250` "
"MPa, :math:`H = 1` GPa."
msgstr ""
"演化方程 :math:`\\dot{\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}}^p = \\dot\\gamma\\, "
"\\mathbf{n}`\\ ，\\ :math:`\\dot\\alpha = \\sqrt{\\tfrac{2}{3}}\\, "
"\\dot\\gamma`\\ 。材料：\\ :math:`E = 200` GPa，\\ :math:`\\nu = 0.3`\\ ，\\ "
":math:`\\sigma_y = 250` MPa，\\ :math:`H = 1` GPa。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:45
#: 3973ebd2b590459d9ccb7b2c5fc1a7a1
msgid "Boundary conditions:"
msgstr "边界条件："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:47
#: b55be26cf7494e6ab862a3caa7ff0829
msgid ":math:`x = 0`: roller (:math:`u_x = 0`),"
msgstr ":math:`x = 0`\\ ：滚动支座（\\ :math:`u_x = 0`\\ ），"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:48
#: c17d2039362445eea15ea452d0eb9d6f
msgid "corner :math:`(0, 0)`: full pin (:math:`u_x = u_y = 0`),"
msgstr "角点 :math:`(0, 0)`\\ ：完全铰接（\\ :math:`u_x = u_y = 0`\\ ），"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:49
#: 7a0b19b9bdb844d987eaae1a9c275570
msgid ""
":math:`x = 1`: prescribed :math:`u_x` ramped from 0 to 0.10 m (10 steps), "
"then back down to 0 (10 more steps)."
msgstr ""
":math:`x = 1`\\ ：规定的 :math:`u_x` 从 0 逐步增加到 0.10 m（10 步），然后再降回 0（再 10 步）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:54
#: e2a2bdea1446467cbb26aff932ac49f7
msgid "Variational constitutive update"
msgstr "变分本构更新"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:56
#: ca4fb9f700c34267a6e0675e6f1eb4a1
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Rather than implementing an explicit \"radial return\" map per quadrature "
"point, the script defines an **algorithmic potential** "
":math:`\\Pi^\\text{alg}(\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}, "
"\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}^p_n, \\alpha_n)` whose stationarity in the "
"plastic variables recovers the standard return-mapping equations. The "
"displacement update at each step is then a single minimization of the "
"integrated potential:"
msgstr ""
"脚本没有为每个求积点实现显式的“径向返回”映射，而是定义了一个 **算法势** "
":math:`\\Pi^\\text{alg}(\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}, "
"\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}^p_n, \\alpha_n)`\\ "
"，它在塑性变量上的驻值条件可还原出标准的返回映射方程。于是每一步的位移更新就是对积分后的势的一次最小化："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:64
#: 10fac061d78846bebbe7475f8eb6dc09
msgid ""
"\\mathbf{u}^{n+1}\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"\\arg\\min_{\\mathbf{u}}\n"
"\\int_\\Omega \\Pi^\\text{alg}\\bigl(\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}(\\mathbf{u}),\\,\n"
"\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}^p_n,\\, \\alpha_n\\bigr)\n"
"\\,\\mathrm{d}\\Omega,"
msgstr ""
"\\mathbf{u}^{n+1}\n"
"\\;=\\;\n"
"\\arg\\min_{\\mathbf{u}}\n"
"\\int_\\Omega \\Pi^\\text{alg}\\bigl(\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}(\\mathbf{u}),\\,\n"
"\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}^p_n,\\, \\alpha_n\\bigr)\n"
"\\,\\mathrm{d}\\Omega,"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:73
#: d9b2a33c0f634eb2bededd12358729bf
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"with autograd providing both the gradient (residual) and, via L-BFGS' "
"implicit Hessian approximation, an effective tangent. After convergence, the"
" history variables :math:`(\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}^p, \\alpha)` are "
"advanced once to the new converged values."
msgstr ""
"由 autograd 提供梯度（残差），并通过 L-BFGS 隐式的海森近似提供一个等效切线刚度。收敛后，历史变量 "
":math:`(\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}^p, \\alpha)` 被一次性推进到新的收敛值。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:79
#: 78db92f419b9483983bad545e2b5d5cc
msgid ""
"The potential is implemented in :class:`~tensormesh.assemble.J2Plasticity`, "
"a built-in shipping in :mod:`tensormesh.assemble`. From the user's side it "
"looks like any other custom assembler:"
msgstr ""
"该势在 :class:`~tensormesh.assemble.J2Plasticity` 中实现，它是 "
":mod:`tensormesh.assemble` 中自带的一个内置类。从用户角度看，它和其他任何自定义装配器没有区别："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:84
#: 1975a77693eb4d28945994edf43a66a7
msgid "examples/solid/plasticity_strip/plasticity_strip.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/solid/plasticity_strip/plasticity_strip.py（核心部分）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:120
#: d31f3383959d471387ddccc29a7ee350
msgid "History variables"
msgstr "历史变量"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:122
#: 2369db463a354ed9849bc1046e1b803e
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"The plastic strain tensor :math:`\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}^p` and the "
"equivalent plastic strain :math:`\\alpha` are stored **per-element / per-"
"quadrature-point**, accessed through ``model.history``. They are passed into"
" the closure as ``element_data`` (per-quadrature, per-element tensors), "
"which TensorMesh dispatches as kwargs to the underlying ``forward`` method "
"exactly the same way ``point_data`` is dispatched (see "
":doc:`../../user_guide/forms`)."
msgstr ""
"塑性应变张量 :math:`\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}^p` 和等效塑性应变 :math:`\\alpha` 按 "
"**逐单元/逐求积点** 存储，通过 ``model.history`` 访问。它们以 ``element_data``\\ "
"（逐求积点、逐单元的张量）的形式传入闭包，TensorMesh 会像分发 ``point_data`` 那样，将其作为关键字参数分发给底层的 "
"``forward`` 方法（参见 :doc:`../../user_guide/forms`\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:131
#: 13e94b83aa884871b7fda03a950f8b32
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"After each load step's L-BFGS converges, the script calls "
"``model.advance_history(u_active)`` which evaluates the converged "
":math:`\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}^p, \\alpha` from the current displacement "
"and overwrites the stored history."
msgstr ""
"在每个载荷步的 L-BFGS 收敛后，脚本调用 ``model.advance_history(u_active)``\\ ，它根据当前位移计算收敛后的"
" :math:`\\boldsymbol{\\varepsilon}^p, \\alpha`\\ ，并覆盖已存储的历史。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:138
#: 21e85500bdb04e2e9178613adb695e26
msgid "Output"
msgstr "输出"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:140
#: 956bda7b2c9a4a42b91b0b4f60611b53
msgid ""
"The script renders a multi-panel animation as ``plasticity_strip.mp4``:"
msgstr "脚本会渲染一段多面板动画，输出为 ``plasticity_strip.mp4``\\ ："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:142
#: fa06680f27ce4adf935d91cdb4dddda5
msgid "deformed mesh, painted by equivalent plastic strain :math:`\\alpha`,"
msgstr "变形后的网格，按等效塑性应变 :math:`\\alpha` 着色，"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:144
#: d6fc1e72c7044206a76883cf965ee62e
msgid ""
"force-displacement curve at the loaded edge, traced through the load / "
"unload cycle."
msgstr "受载边缘处的力-位移曲线，贯穿整个加载/卸载循环。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:147
#: b0cc8aaa33c8465d9dba60f284edd99c
msgid ""
"The force-displacement curve is the canonical signature of plasticity: "
"linear elastic loading until yield, a hardening branch above "
":math:`\\sigma_y`, then a linear elastic unloading branch back to a non-zero"
" residual displacement at zero load."
msgstr ""
"力-位移曲线是塑性的典型标志：线弹性加载直至屈服，超过 :math:`\\sigma_y` "
"后进入硬化段，随后是线弹性卸载段，在零载荷处回到一个非零的残余位移。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:160
#: 90a06e4a895543768e4a0afd30c903b5
msgid ""
"*Output of* ``plasticity_strip.py``\\ *: the strip deforms under the "
"prescribed elongation (left panel, colored by equivalent plastic strain* "
":math:`\\alpha`\\ *) while the force-displacement curve at the loaded edge "
"(right panel) traces the load / unload cycle — elastic loading to yield, the"
" hardening branch, then elastic unloading back to a permanent residual "
"displacement at zero load.*"
msgstr ""
"*``plasticity_strip.py`` 的输出：钢条在规定的伸长下变形（左面板，按等效塑性应变* :math:`\\alpha` "
"*着色），同时受载边缘处的力-位移曲线（右面板）描绘出加载/卸载循环——弹性加载至屈服、硬化段，然后弹性卸载回到零载荷处的永久残余位移。*"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:169
#: dca8073c083c43f78297e953d4fd5e3a
msgid "Going to 3D"
msgstr "扩展到三维"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:171
#: 934dac5725a44497add9614f8740cbd9
#, python-format, no-python-format
msgid ""
":class:`~tensormesh.assemble.J2Plasticity` is dimension-generic, so the same"
" constitutive model, variational-update pattern, and history-variable "
"bookkeeping carry over to 3D unchanged. The script "
"``examples/solid/plasticity_3d/plasticity_3d.py`` runs J2 flow on a "
":math:`0.5 \\times 0.5 \\times 0.5` m steel cube, stretched 40 % in the "
":math:`x` direction over 50 loading steps and unloaded over 50 more. Only "
"the *driver* differs from the 2D strip:"
msgstr ""
":class:`~tensormesh.assemble.J2Plasticity` "
"是维度无关的，因此同样的本构模型、变分更新模式和历史变量记账都能原封不动地搬到三维。脚本 "
"``examples/solid/plasticity_3d/plasticity_3d.py`` 在一个 :math:`0.5 \\times 0.5"
" \\times 0.5` m 的钢制立方体上运行 J2 流动，在 :math:`x` 方向上经 50 个加载步拉伸 40 %，再经 50 "
"步卸载。与二维钢条相比，只有 *驱动脚本* 不同："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:179
#: 8c3fac284ffa4df6b2d5f3cba16d6e84
msgid "examples/solid/plasticity_3d/plasticity_3d.py (essence)"
msgstr "examples/solid/plasticity_3d/plasticity_3d.py（核心部分）"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:190
#: 04c07a23d35d469cb8299e0967f23b91
msgid "What actually changes is scale, not the model:"
msgstr "真正改变的是规模，而不是模型："

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:192
#: 60e1cd7401714c2cbb6c2df50b39e74f
msgid ""
"**3D mesh.** ``gen_cube`` produces a tetrahedral cube with on the order of "
"5–10 k DOFs (vs. ~3 k in the 2D strip); each L-BFGS iteration integrates "
"over many more quadrature points."
msgstr ""
"**三维网格。** ``gen_cube`` 生成一个四面体立方体，自由度约为 5–10 k 量级（相比之下二维钢条约为 3 k）；每次 L-BFGS "
"迭代都要在多得多的求积点上积分。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:195
#: 94bddd993bc34043848c30a5db1ea366
#, python-format
msgid ""
"**More load steps.** 50 loading + 50 unloading = 100 steps, reaching 40 % "
"strain — far enough that the hardening branch dominates. At 40 % nominal "
"strain the small-strain assumption is being stretched (literally): the "
"example is a useful regression test of the J2 model, but do not trust "
"absolute stress numbers far from the elastic regime."
msgstr ""
"**更多载荷步。** 50 步加载 + 50 步卸载 = 100 步，达到 40 % 的应变——足以让硬化段占据主导。在 40 % "
"名义应变下，小应变假设已被（字面意义上地）拉伸到极限：该示例是 J2 模型一个有用的回归测试，但不要在远离弹性区的情况下信任应力的绝对数值。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:201
#: 51a0050f3f8f4a62bf160da732ee1ee7
msgid ""
"**Output.** ``plasticity_3d_combined.mp4`` shows the deformed cube colored "
"by **von Mises stress** plus a force-displacement curve at the loaded face."
msgstr ""
"**输出。** ``plasticity_3d_combined.mp4`` 展示了按 **冯·米塞斯应力** 着色的变形立方体，以及受载面处的力-"
"位移曲线。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:205
#: 8b068ee1ac264b1f856b789ab27bb322
msgid ""
"The 3D run is L-BFGS-bound — most wall-clock time is the per-iteration "
"energy evaluation and autograd backward. Moving the optimization to a GPU "
"(``mesh.to(\"cuda\")``, ``u.to(\"cuda\")``) helps significantly, and the "
"assembler's ``batch_size`` argument chunks the per-quadrature integrand if "
"memory becomes tight (see :doc:`../../user_guide/batched_workflows`)."
msgstr ""
"三维运行的瓶颈在 L-BFGS——大部分实际耗时都花在每次迭代的能量计算和 autograd 反向传播上。把优化迁移到 GPU（\\ "
"``mesh.to(\"cuda\")``\\ 、\\ ``u.to(\"cuda\")``\\ ）能显著提速；当显存吃紧时，装配器的 "
"``batch_size`` 参数可对逐求积点的被积项分块处理（参见 "
":doc:`../../user_guide/batched_workflows`\\ ）。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:220
#: 636cc88e6d0b474ea6f2e5f17fbbe525
#, python-format, no-python-format
msgid ""
"*Output of* ``plasticity_3d.py``\\ *: the steel cube stretched to 40 % "
"strain (left panel, colored by von Mises stress) and the force-displacement "
"curve at the loaded face (right panel) over the 50-step load / 50-step "
"unload cycle — the 3D counterpart of the strip animation above.*"
msgstr ""
"*``plasticity_3d.py`` 的输出：钢制立方体被拉伸至 40 % 应变（左面板，按冯·米塞斯应力着色），以及在 50 步加载/50 "
"步卸载循环中受载面处的力-位移曲线（右面板）——这是上面钢条动画的三维对应版本。*"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:233
#: 2ec0f90f258f4475ac94e2f6c522d582
msgid "Running it"
msgstr "运行示例"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:240
#: 1a2b988a91fa47c4910b04e19cc825e5
msgid ""
"Console output reports per-step force, displacement, and maximum plastic "
"strain."
msgstr "控制台输出会逐步报告力、位移和最大塑性应变。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:245
#: c6565045c4184ebd94514c9a360bf169
msgid "What's next"
msgstr "下一步"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:247
#: 615d52697ba345028168bc6bf8aa33a9
msgid ""
":doc:`hyperelastic_beam` — the same L-BFGS-with-history pattern but for a "
"*path-independent* (hyperelastic) energy."
msgstr ":doc:`hyperelastic_beam` —— 同样的“带历史的 L-BFGS”模式，但针对的是 *路径无关* 的（超弹性）能量。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:249
#: 8196637193a5476bb23fbacd35ebe7d4
msgid ""
":doc:`hertzian_contact` — another non-quadratic energy driver, this time a "
"contact penalty."
msgstr ":doc:`hertzian_contact` —— 另一个非二次能量驱动，这次是接触罚函数。"

#: ../../source/example_gallery/solid/plasticity_strip.rst:251
#: d67edc813db1494d85164f7819083027
msgid ""
":doc:`../../user_guide/batched_workflows` — chunking the per-quadrature "
"integrand for the larger 3D problem."
msgstr ":doc:`../../user_guide/batched_workflows` —— 对更大的三维问题中逐求积点的被积项进行分块。"

